des:
Now with just a touch on your phone screen or other device, voice apps let you jump right in to Blueprint content, find out how to subscribe, advertise or have your daughter or son be a part of the program or how to contribute content for this extraordinary experience that provides students with the power of the pen and lens and imagination to conduct real world reporting, writing, graphics arts skills and more in the pursuit of ethics based journalism. 

This high impact, performance based, product producing program reaches to and beyond the local community providing readers/viewers/listeners with probative, poignant and rich inroads to youth news, culture, creativity and varied capabilities, as it paves the way for student participant's entry into adult world, professional proficiency. 

Many Blueprint alum have found the skills they gained invaluable in their various career paths which have been in diplomacy, political speech writing, communications, marketing, print, tv and audio broadcast journalism , illustration, a.i. futures, education, public service and more, along with building the capabilities, strength of character, and confidence so valuable to engage in and enhance leading human interaction and leadership based on values of equity, fairness and objectivity.
